steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
Debug step:
When I navigate to menu "Database" with submenu "Database Editor"
Then I should see Database screen display
When I add new table with Name "jitapi009" and Comment "Testing autofill"
Then I should see the table with Name "jitapi009" display
When I navigate to menu "API" with submenu "API endpoints"
Then I should see API screen display
When I select api name "jitapi009s" from list
When I edit API method "GET" with endpoint "/api/jitapi009s"
When I click tab "Request params" in Params of floating panel
When I input Auto-fill not verified with json payload `empty`
Then I should see the warning popup with message "Please Enter valid json.."
When I close the modal popup
When I input Auto-fill not verified with json payload `{invalid}`
Then I should see the warning popup with message "Please Enter valid json.."
When I close the modal popup
When I input Auto-fill and verified with json payload `{}`
Then I should see floating panel has Params - row "1" - value "","".
When I input Auto-fill and verified with json payload `{"harry":"String"}`
Then I should see floating panel has Params - row "1" - value "harry","String".
When I input Auto-fill and verified with json payload `{"harry":"invalid"}`
Then I should see floating panel has Params - row "1" - value "harry","String".
When I input Auto-fill and verified with json payload `{"harry":{"harry_child":"String"}}`
When I expand the row name "harry"
Then I should see floating panel has Params - row "1" - value "harry","Object(JSON)".
Then I should see floating panel has Params - row "2" - value "harry_child","String".
When I close the floating panel
When I edit API method "GET" with endpoint "/api/jitapi009s/:id"
When I click tab "Request params" in Params of floating panel
When I input Auto-fill not verified with json payload `empty`
Then I should see the warning popup with message "Please Enter valid json.."
When I close the modal popup
When I input Auto-fill not verified with json payload `{invalid}`
Then I should see the warning popup with message "Please Enter valid json.."
When I close the modal popup
When I input Auto-fill not verified with json payload `{}`
Then I should see floating panel has Params - row "1" - value "","".
When I input Auto-fill not verified with json payload `{"harry":"String"}`
Then I should see floating panel has Params - row "1" - value "harry","String".
When I input Auto-fill not verified with json payload `{"harry":"invalid"}`
Then I should see floating panel has Params - row "1" - value "harry","String".
When I input Auto-fill not verified with json payload `{"harry":{"harry_child":"String"}}`
When I expand the row name "harry"
Then I should see floating panel has Params - row "1" - value "harry","Object(JSON)".
